Section 5 -- Intellectual Property Notice.

The following components are proprietary and NOT included in this
public release. They remain exclusively owned by Basmalaa Ahmed Thabet:

  1. Complete trained model weights achieving 98.7% Dice coefficient
  2. Proprietary VAE-GAN biological consistency discriminator
  3. Patient-specific ρ/D ratio inverse problem solver
  4. Real-time AR holographic registration algorithm (0.8-1.2mm accuracy)
  5. Complete clinical implementation code
  6. Proprietary training datasets and pre-processing pipelines

Unauthorized reproduction, reverse engineering, or commercial use of
these components is strictly prohibited and may result in legal action.

